tasks with network diagrams and matrices Okoe, Mershack, Radu Jianu, and Stephen G. Kobourov. <a href=\"https://www2.cs.arizona.edu/~kobourov/NL-AM-TVCG18.pdf\">\"Node-link or Adjacency Matrices: Old Question, New Insights.\"</a> <em>IEEE transactions on visualization and computer graphics</em> (2018).</p>\n<a href=\"#fnref-2\" class=\"footnote-backref\">↩</a>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>","excerpt":"is a visualization of entities and their relationships that together form a network structure. Each entity is a node, and each connection…","overview":"<p>is a visualization of entities and their relationships that together form a network structure. Each entity is a node, and each connection…</p>","fields":{"variationOf":null},"frontmatter":{"title":"network diagram","synonyms":["node-link diagram","vertex-edge diagram","network graph"],"functions":["network of relationships"],"visualizationTechniques":[{"techniqueId":"CON","informationType":"relationships between entities","axisDirection":null}],"informationTypes":null,"axisDirections":null,"examples":[{"title":"Chart of Neural Networks","link":"http://www.asimovinstitute.org/neural-network-zoo/","note":null,"image":"types-of-neural-networks.png"},{"title":"The Strengths of Nations","link":"http://wbpaley.com/brad/mapOfScience/index.html","note":null,"image":"the-strengths-of-nations.jpg"},{"title":"How Scientific Paradigms Relate","link":"http://wbpaley.com/brad/mapOfScience/index.html","note":null,"image":"how-scientific-paradigms-relate.jpg"},{"title":"Most Common Family Types in America","link":"https://flowingdata.com/2016/07/20/modern-family-structure/","note":null,"image":"family-types.png"}],"tools":null},"fileInfo":{"__typename":"File","modifiedTime":"07/24/2023"}},"coverImage":{"publicURL":"/static/e295f8c7a507914a10c8a149f51fc986/cover.png"},"anatomyImage":{"publicURL":"/static/17d24d2806cfaeaa97922d00b0d119e8/anatomy.png"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://graphopedia.xyz"}},"exampleImages":{"edges":[{"no